data.description: Make an appointment to see this beautiful -TURN-KEY- Impressive 3-bedroom, 2.5-bath townhome in Baytown Square: a gated community. This location is conveniently within 1 mile of (I-75) and offers quick access to many local Sarasota amenities, including lifestyle activities. You will experience natural lighting and tranquil views from within the doors of this end-unit home built in 2018. You will enjoy views of a serene and private preserve when you step onto the lanai. The downstairs living area flows flawlessly into the kitchen's open layout, allowing for seamless entertainment and easy interaction with guests while preparing meals and socializing. You will find the bedrooms on the second floor, each with ample space. The primary ensuite has a walk-in closet and shower. The community has a pool and clubhouse for residents, including a low monthly HOA fee. Do your research, compare other properties with similar square footage and year built in the 34240 zip code, and make an appointment to see this property.
